365
00:40:58,000 --> 00:40:59,923
(CROWD CHEERING)

366
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:02,842
DAVE: Do it! Go!

367
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:05,086
That's it.

368
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:12,651
(WHISTLE BLOWS)

369
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:16,043
MAN: Attack! Attack! Control his rolling.
Control his rolling.

370
00:41:16,240 --> 00:41:18,402
DAVE: Keep your elbows in!

371
00:41:22,800 --> 00:41:24,962
(CROWD CHEERING)

372
00:41:27,080 --> 00:41:28,411
(WHISTLE BLOWS)

373
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:33,006
(APPLAUSE)

374
00:41:37,520 --> 00:41:39,170
ANNOUNCER: Mark Schultz.

375
00:41:39,360 --> 00:41:40,441
(CROWD CHEERING)

376
00:41:40,640 --> 00:41:42,290
Good job, Mark.

377
00:42:00,360 --> 00:42:02,886
(MAN SPEAKING IN FRENCH)

378
00:42:13,600 --> 00:42:15,204
ANNOUNCER: Dave Schultz.

379
00:42:16,200 --> 00:42:19,283
(CROWD CHEERING)

380
00:42:47,240 --> 00:42:49,049
(CROWD CHEERING)

381
00:43:00,480 --> 00:43:03,290
(WHISTLE BLOWS AND CROWD CHEERING)

382
