654
01:01:55,680 --> 01:01:58,001
BOTH: Ornithologist,
philatelist, philanthropist.

655
01:01:58,160 --> 01:01:59,207
JOHN: Again.

656
01:01:59,400 --> 01:02:01,641
BOTH: Ornithologist,
philatelist, philanthropist.

657
01:02:01,800 --> 01:02:02,847
JOHN: Good.

