672
01:02:50,120 --> 01:02:51,963
Impressive. Isn't
that impressive?

673
01:02:52,160 --> 01:02:53,764
Congratulations. Thank you.

674
01:02:53,920 --> 01:02:55,604
Quite a young man.

675
01:02:55,760 --> 01:02:57,728
Very proud of him.
Nice meeting you.

676
01:03:07,640 --> 01:03:11,611
